msg: The change in WSCOMMONS-485 implies that XOP decoding is always done at the same level (i.e. between the underlying parser and XOPAwareStAXOMBuilder/MTOMStAXSOAPModelBuilder). There is therefore no need any more for StreamingOMSerializer to do XOP decoding.
